Each row in the dataset represents a loan applicant and contains multiple attributes describing their personal, financial, and credit information.

       Feature                                             Description

1.   Applicant_ID---------------------------------------Unique applicant ID

2.   Applicant_Income-----------------------------------Monthly income of applicant

3.   Coapplicant_Income---------------------------------Monthly income of co-applicant

4.   Employment_Status----------------------------------Salaried / Self-Employed / Business

5.   Age------------------------------------------------Applicant age

6.   Marital_Status-------------------------------------Married / Single

7.   Dependents-----------------------------------------Number of dependents

8.   Credit_Score---------------------------------------Credit bureau score

9.   Existing_Loans-------------------------------------Number of already running loans

10.  DTI_Ratio------------------------------------------Debt-to-Income ratio

11.  Savings--------------------------------------------Savings balance

12.  Collateral_Value-----------------------------------Value of collateral provided

13.  Loan_Amount----------------------------------------Loan amount requested

14.  Loan_Term------------------------------------------Loan duration (months)

15.  Loan_Purpose---------------------------------------Home / Education / Personal / Business

16.  Property_Area--------------------------------------Urban / Semi-Urban / Rural

17.  Education_Level------------------------------------Graduate / Postgraduate / Undergraduate

18.  Gender---------------------------------------------Male / Female

19.  Employer_Category----------------------------------Govt / Private / Self

20.  Loan_Approved--------------------------------------Yes = Approved, No = Rejected